text: X-Large () is a 2011 Egyptian romantic comedy movie directed by Sherif Arafah and starring Ahmed Helmy, Sayed Mustafa, Donia Samir Ghanem, Ibrahim Nasr, Yasmin Raeis, Said Tarabeek, Nahed El Sebai. ==Other websites== * Category:2011 romantic comedy movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:Movies directed by Sherif Arafah
